{
  "stem": "11184.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was worse, because they-- they give you that little food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What you got was hardly enough to survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people that worked still had some extra money to buy extra.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't that type.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] No.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, I never-- well, you couldn't-- a large ghetto, you couldn't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could never.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was too watched-over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, very seldom, I don't think any-- you approached it only-- you know, you-- you got killed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You close to that border.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the gate it was-- it was a--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Upstairs-- I mean, what you call?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A bridge-- a bridge-- a bridge, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I don't remember--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--working.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Day after day, you know-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --you know, we had neighbors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we visited and talked to neighbors, you know-- and hoping that it's going to get better.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, and then people gave up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, nobody--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--was positive, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody was positive anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed in the ghetto till 1944, a year later.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like 11 months, you know, after my father died.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, it was July-- I think the beginning of July.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what I think it was, July.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1944.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were-- there was supposed-- when-- in-- in 1944, there was selections were taking place every few months.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we all had to be in it-- all of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, if they find you, they're going to kill you-- if they find you in a-- in a room.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they also, in-- in-- in '43, they took away my aunt, my uncle, and my cousins-- young cousins, you know, and my mother's brothers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The whole family went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't know where they did-- where they took them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were taken out.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
